A budget is just a tool to put every single dollar to work in order to FREE yourself from the restrictions of money forever.'.

node.text:
Too many have the wrong perception of Budgets. 

Yes, they encourage you to make smarter short term financial decisions at the expense of freely spending your money as you see fit, but that’s so you can free yourself from money long term and never have to worry about money again. 

Living paycheck to paycheck with a bunch of debt is more restrictive long term compared to a budget. 

A budget is not meant to restrict you financially for life, it’s a tool to help you build long term wealth and escape the restrictions of money forever. 💯
“There are old investors, and there are bold investors, but there are no old bold investors.” - Marks
Kind of crazy to think about how much opportunity is now available to everyone thanks to the internet. I still think it’s vastly underrated.. it’s never been easier to self educate 💯

Send this to all of the SAVERS! 

Long term wealth is built by investing, not saving! 

You are actually losing money each year by keeping your money in a savings account due to inflation. Make sure your money is working hard for you!

**This example is assuming a 10% per year average return for investing.**
Making money pays the bills. Investing money sets you free from money. 💯

node.text:
Doing this was life changing. 

Keep your focus on the things that you can control. 

Don’t give anything else your energy. 

Everything else is just outside noise.

TAX TIP: If you own a business/self employed, and have an office you use specifically for business, you can still claim the “home office deduction” even if you’re renting. 

Hope this tip helps a few people out who did not know this! 🔥

Want to learn more about the tax code? Give the tax expert @doughertytaxsolutions a follow!
Happy Friday! Just a reminder to buy some assets if you got paid today. I just bought some more $VOO and $QQQ today. What did you buy?

Nothing else comes even close!

Buy assets, and let those assets pay for the lifestyle you want later. 💯🔥
